Package: methylkey
Title: Analysis of DNA Methylation from Illumina Methylation Arrays
Version: 0.4.1.0000
Date: 2026-05-29
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Vincent",
           family = "Cahais",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cahaisv@iarc.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5530-4368"))
Author: Vincent Cahais
Maintainer: Vincent Cahais <cahaisv@iarc.fr>
Description: Comprehensive Bioconductor package for analysis of DNA methylation
    data from Illumina methylation arrays. Provides preprocessing pipelines using
    both sesame and minfi packages for 27k, 450k, EPIC and mouse arrays. Includes
    functionality for quality control, differential methylation analysis, DMR
    detection and visualization.
